WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.710
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.230 --> 02:49.920
[Episode 3]

02:50.780 --> 02:53.990
[Cold Spring Palace, Demon Race]

02:56.570 --> 02:57.520
You mean

02:57.930 --> 02:59.220
a human

02:59.410 --> 03:01.160
absorbed the Desireless Stone into her body?

03:02.250 --> 03:03.850
I saw it with my own eyes.

03:03.880 --> 03:06.000
That Eternal from Lanling tried hard to get it out,

03:06.020 --> 03:07.390
but he couldn't.

03:15.670 --> 03:16.670
Grand Master,

03:16.870 --> 03:18.970
the Master of Bright Moon Palace is in Ning'an City,

03:19.030 --> 03:20.280
but he lets that human

03:20.280 --> 03:21.990
come and go freely with the Desireless Stone.

03:22.010 --> 03:23.290
Unless they're colluding,

03:23.320 --> 03:25.040
it could only be that even Fan Yue

03:25.060 --> 03:26.460
can't do anything about her.

03:27.010 --> 03:28.450
Go bring that human back.

03:28.480 --> 03:29.650
Yes, Grand Master.

03:30.810 --> 03:31.980
One more thing,

03:32.600 --> 03:34.880
last night, I spread the Nether Poison in Ning'an City,

03:34.900 --> 03:36.340
but it seems

03:36.370 --> 03:37.890
it didn't work as expected.

03:38.370 --> 03:39.970
Lady Fu Ling,

03:40.000 --> 03:41.590
you're complaining too soon.

03:49.410 --> 03:52.230
[Chen Ye, demon of Cold Spring Palace]

03:49.510 --> 03:50.470
Grand Master,

03:50.490 --> 03:51.650
the Lion Clan has been wiped out.

03:51.680 --> 03:52.930
Their leader's inner core is here.

03:52.950 --> 03:54.100
It can help you heal your wounds.

03:54.130 --> 03:55.130
Please take a look.

04:03.240 --> 04:03.910
Chen Ye,

04:03.910 --> 04:04.870
well done!

04:05.480 --> 04:06.800
You never left Cold Spring Palace

04:06.840 --> 04:07.800
but could

04:07.800 --> 04:09.360
win from thousands of miles away.

04:09.640 --> 04:10.520
Impressive.

04:11.230 --> 04:12.630
The Nether Poison was lost for many years.

04:12.660 --> 04:14.130
I studied it for years

04:14.170 --> 04:15.920
to bring it back into the world.

04:15.940 --> 04:17.399
Lady Fu Ling,

04:17.430 --> 04:18.899
if you want to know if it works,

04:18.920 --> 04:20.360
why not ask me directly?

04:21.019 --> 04:23.490
Then let me ask you.

04:24.010 --> 04:25.450
The Nether Poison was released last night.

04:25.480 --> 04:27.560
Why hasn't it taken effect yet?

04:27.580 --> 04:28.850
Could it be

04:28.880 --> 04:31.090
your years of hard work have failed?

04:47.520 --> 04:49.270
Lady Fu Ling, do you think

04:49.290 --> 04:50.670
it's effective now?

04:57.840 --> 04:58.860
Noisy.

04:59.540 --> 05:00.980
The Nether Poison is incurable.

05:01.010 --> 05:03.060
Once poisoned, there is no escape.

05:03.240 --> 05:04.920
He should thank you

05:04.950 --> 05:06.560
for helping him find peace.

05:06.580 --> 05:07.900
Since it works,

05:07.930 --> 05:09.930
why hasn't anything happened in Ning'an City?

05:09.950 --> 05:11.900
Naturally, it's because I controlled the dosage.

05:12.250 --> 05:13.640
In the dead of night,

05:13.670 --> 05:15.110
the person lying next to you

05:15.160 --> 05:17.190
is the one who brings your death.

05:17.320 --> 05:19.080
Isn't that more interesting?

05:24.920 --> 05:26.010
My Lord.

05:27.050 --> 05:28.660
My Lord, what's that sound?

05:29.480 --> 05:30.600
My Lord.

05:38.920 --> 05:39.820
Interesting?

05:40.290 --> 05:42.190
You're just bored after being stuck in this palace

05:42.190 --> 05:42.920
for too long!

05:42.920 --> 05:44.510
After all, I'm not like you,

05:44.540 --> 05:46.000
who have traveled far and wide

05:46.020 --> 05:47.020
but still haven't

05:47.050 --> 05:48.280
killed Fan Yue

05:48.300 --> 05:49.860
for Grand Master.

05:49.890 --> 05:50.370
You…

05:50.390 --> 05:51.790
Alright, alright.

05:52.920 --> 05:53.950
You two

05:54.330 --> 05:56.260
came to Cold Spring Palace at the same time

05:56.409 --> 05:58.140
and grew up together.

05:58.170 --> 05:59.560
Playful banter is fine,

05:59.580 --> 06:01.630
but don't let it distract you from the important matters.

06:02.110 --> 06:03.060
Yes, Grand Master.

06:03.390 --> 06:05.300
I'll bring back Bai Shuo.

06:05.330 --> 06:06.430
I'll never forget

06:06.450 --> 06:07.570
your revenge, Grand Master.

06:07.600 --> 06:08.770
Once the Nether Poison takes effect,

06:08.790 --> 06:10.910
Fan Yue will be hunted by the whole Eternal Race

06:10.940 --> 06:11.850
with no way out.

06:12.840 --> 06:13.400
Good.

06:14.330 --> 06:15.160
You may leave.

06:21.970 --> 06:22.680
Master.

06:23.210 --> 06:23.820
What's it?

06:24.140 --> 06:25.030
Last night,

06:25.060 --> 06:26.500
there were other demons in the city.

06:26.880 --> 06:27.810
Judging by how they did things,

06:27.830 --> 06:28.950
they're from Cold Spring Palace.

06:29.590 --> 06:31.330
Zhen Yu couldn't sit still any longer.

06:31.700 --> 06:34.030
But I'm not sure if they're after the Desireless Stone

06:34.700 --> 06:36.020
or if they're after you.

06:36.320 --> 06:37.690
It doesn't matter what they're after.

06:38.510 --> 06:40.510
Five years ago, I cut off his tail.

06:40.570 --> 06:41.930
If he dares to come again,

06:42.560 --> 06:44.310
I'll cut off his head.

06:46.980 --> 06:49.210
I've bought Father all his favorite food.

06:49.240 --> 06:50.170
His birthday's the day after tomorrow.

06:50.190 --> 06:51.310
He'll definitely be happy.

06:52.980 --> 06:53.610
Zhao?

06:54.520 --> 06:55.230
Zhao?

06:56.450 --> 06:57.250
What's wrong?

06:57.270 --> 06:58.620
What's wrong with you?

06:58.750 --> 07:00.340
You've been distracted today.

07:00.750 --> 07:02.070
Making steamed buns last night tired you out?

07:02.650 --> 07:04.480
There's something I can't figure out,

07:04.500 --> 07:05.400
so I couldn't sleep.

07:05.780 --> 07:06.780
What is it?

07:06.800 --> 07:07.610
Tell me.

07:07.640 --> 07:08.570
I'll help you think it through.

07:08.590 --> 07:09.410
It's nothing,

07:09.440 --> 07:10.320
just business stuff.

07:10.930 --> 07:11.810
Listen,

07:11.830 --> 07:13.220
don't overwork yourself.

07:13.350 --> 07:14.870
Business is important,

07:14.890 --> 07:16.470
but your health comes first.

07:16.500 --> 07:17.980
Father is just like you.

07:18.000 --> 07:19.200
Once he gets caught up in work,

07:19.230 --> 07:20.870
he stays up all night,

07:20.890 --> 07:22.950
wearing himself out and ending up with health problems.

07:23.860 --> 07:24.930
Zhao,

07:24.960 --> 07:26.630
talk to him more

07:26.660 --> 07:27.910
and ask him to sleep

07:27.930 --> 07:29.000
and eat on time.

07:29.520 --> 07:31.320
You've always cared about Uncle Bai.

07:31.340 --> 07:32.370
Why don't you

07:32.400 --> 07:33.960
say these things to him yourself?

07:35.280 --> 07:36.770
If I talk to him myself,

07:37.420 --> 07:39.300
we'll just end up arguing again.

07:39.800 --> 07:40.680
He's more likely

07:40.710 --> 07:42.380
to listen to you than to me.

07:42.460 --> 07:43.970
When I'm not around,

07:43.990 --> 07:45.310
please look after him for me.

07:45.970 --> 07:47.040
Not around?

07:47.060 --> 07:48.000
Where are you…

07:54.180 --> 07:55.030
Don't bite me!

08:08.570 --> 08:09.740
He looks familiar.

08:16.690 --> 08:18.510
I made them take detoxifying pills that night.

08:18.960 --> 08:19.860
How could this happen?

08:20.890 --> 08:21.960
Take him away.

08:22.430 --> 08:22.950
Move!

08:24.170 --> 08:24.750
Bai Yu.

08:27.530 --> 08:28.530
What's going on?

08:28.560 --> 08:29.190
Lady Shuo.

08:29.210 --> 08:29.970
Mr. Chong Zhao.

08:30.500 --> 08:31.770
Last night, for some unknown reason,

08:31.800 --> 08:33.049
some people in the city went mad.

08:33.070 --> 08:33.720
Seven or eight of them

08:33.750 --> 08:34.870
showed the exact same symptoms—

08:34.890 --> 08:35.679
complete loss of sanity,

08:35.710 --> 08:36.549
biting people all around.

08:36.580 --> 08:37.350
Very dangerous.

08:37.760 --> 08:38.679
What about my father?

08:38.710 --> 08:40.309
He sent for doctors first thing this morning.

08:40.330 --> 08:41.730
They're treating the sick now.

08:42.179 --> 08:42.820
I have to go

08:42.850 --> 08:43.860
make a patrol now.

08:47.390 --> 08:48.120
Shuo,

08:48.140 --> 08:49.410
I need to leave the city for a bit.

08:49.440 --> 08:50.390
You go back first.

08:50.410 --> 08:51.440
Suddenly?

08:51.470 --> 08:52.350
I'll be back soon.

08:54.100 --> 08:55.090
It's unsafe outside!

08:55.120 --> 08:56.170
Be careful.

09:25.170 --> 09:26.080
Physician Chen.

09:28.160 --> 09:28.890
Governor.

09:29.180 --> 09:30.590
Have you found a way to treat them?

09:31.190 --> 09:32.310
We've practiced medicine for over a decade

09:32.330 --> 09:33.420
but never seen a disease like this.

09:33.450 --> 09:35.210
We really don't know how to treat it.

09:35.230 --> 09:37.020
Then figure something out!

09:37.050 --> 09:38.370
They must be cured!

09:38.540 --> 09:39.380
This city must not

09:39.400 --> 09:40.500
fall into chaos!

09:40.710 --> 09:41.630
-Yes.
-Yes.

09:41.670 --> 09:42.630
We'll do our best.

09:42.660 --> 09:43.680
We'll do our best.

09:50.720 --> 09:51.720
Chong Zhao.

09:52.930 --> 09:53.980
Chong Zhao.

09:54.570 --> 09:55.440
Le Zhu.

09:55.440 --> 09:57.120
There's no meeting today.

09:56.050 --> 09:57.880
[Le Zhu, Eternal Race, Lanling Sect]

09:57.140 --> 09:58.410
Why are you suddenly back?

09:58.480 --> 09:59.930
I need to meet my master and uncles.

09:59.960 --> 10:01.670
Don't meet them now.

10:02.830 --> 10:03.500
Why?

10:04.010 --> 10:05.560
Well,

10:05.590 --> 10:06.750
something happened.

10:07.090 --> 10:08.050
What happened?

10:08.510 --> 10:10.110
Last night, an eternal envoy sent a message

10:10.130 --> 10:11.030
that a few Lanling disciples

10:11.030 --> 10:12.840
were killed in the human realm.

10:13.450 --> 10:14.660
Upon investigation,

10:14.680 --> 10:16.000
they were killed by demons.

10:17.130 --> 10:18.220
Who sent them?

10:18.380 --> 10:19.740
We don't know yet.

10:19.770 --> 10:21.990
Sect Leader, Feng Yu, and Yan Huo

10:22.030 --> 10:23.390
have gone to find it out.

10:23.420 --> 10:25.740
Yu Feng and Jing Lei were shocked and furious.

10:25.770 --> 10:27.300
They're still angry right now.

10:27.320 --> 10:29.720
If it's not urgent,

10:29.750 --> 10:31.420
you'd better report it another time.

10:31.440 --> 10:32.360
Well,

10:32.390 --> 10:32.870
Yu Feng,

10:32.900 --> 10:33.770
write it down for me.

10:33.790 --> 10:35.940
Tomorrow, I'll go to the demons and…

10:37.300 --> 10:38.100
Uncles.

10:38.130 --> 10:38.670
Why are you back?

10:38.670 --> 10:40.120
Has something happened in Ning'an City?

10:40.780 --> 10:42.580
A few demons have caused a stir

10:42.600 --> 10:43.540
in Ning'an City.

10:43.800 --> 10:44.720
I was planning

10:44.750 --> 10:46.590
to ask Master how we should handle it.

10:46.610 --> 10:47.460
Demons again?

10:48.130 --> 10:49.840
Demons broke the rules between the two races

10:49.870 --> 10:51.160
and killed Eternals.

10:51.180 --> 10:51.700
Chong Zhao.

10:52.230 --> 10:54.260
Any demon who breaks the rules

10:54.290 --> 10:55.500
must be severely punished.

10:57.760 --> 10:58.960
Uncles,

10:58.990 --> 11:00.690
there's one more thing I need to ask.

11:00.710 --> 11:01.660
What is it?

11:01.680 --> 11:03.320
The Desireless Stone is somewhere out there.

11:03.350 --> 11:04.380
If

11:04.400 --> 11:05.790
it has chosen a master,

11:05.900 --> 11:07.820
how should the Eternal Race do?

11:07.850 --> 11:10.690
An ancient artifact that's been dormant for 60,000 years

11:10.710 --> 11:11.620
has chosen a master?

11:11.650 --> 11:12.500
Who could it choose?

11:13.120 --> 11:15.160
Are you suggesting the divine race still exists?

11:16.210 --> 11:17.490
What if

11:17.520 --> 11:18.620
it did choose a master?

11:19.180 --> 11:20.420
That's simple.

11:20.440 --> 11:22.700
If it's an Eternal, they should be brought under our sect.

11:22.730 --> 11:23.890
If it's a demon,

11:23.910 --> 11:25.320
they should be killed on the spot.

11:28.180 --> 11:29.370
And if it's a human?

11:29.450 --> 11:31.740
Human? They don't have that kind of power.

11:32.640 --> 11:34.040
Just saying, what if?

11:34.060 --> 11:35.850
Humans can be easily controlled by demons.

11:35.880 --> 11:37.620
A human with the Desireless Stone

11:37.640 --> 11:39.060
must be killed.

11:41.160 --> 11:41.850
Stop.

11:43.530 --> 11:44.480
If you break it again,

11:44.510 --> 11:45.850
I won't have any pen left.

11:45.880 --> 11:47.520
How many pens have you broken this month?

11:47.540 --> 11:48.730
-Give it to me.
-Do you still have money to deduct?

11:48.760 --> 11:50.000
Don't grab me.

11:50.030 --> 11:50.630
Stop breaking my pen.

11:50.630 --> 11:51.390
Then I'll break your leg.

11:51.390 --> 11:52.550
What did I owe you?

12:01.690 --> 12:03.630
Why hasn't Father come back?

12:04.300 --> 12:05.700
Has something happened?

12:39.670 --> 12:40.600
Who are you?

12:40.950 --> 12:42.160
A mere human

12:42.180 --> 12:43.360
with an iron dagger,

12:43.390 --> 12:45.120
and yet you think you can defend against me.

12:45.140 --> 12:46.140
A human?

12:47.660 --> 12:48.850
You're not human?

12:48.910 --> 12:50.960
Since you know I'm not human,

12:50.980 --> 12:52.530
I suggest you surrender

12:52.560 --> 12:53.800
and come with me.

12:53.870 --> 12:54.600
Go where?

12:55.120 --> 12:56.700
You're asking too many questions.

13:20.890 --> 13:21.980
Cloud Fire Arrows.

13:23.580 --> 13:25.030
Fu Ling from Cold Spring Palace.

13:26.020 --> 13:27.070
Who's she?

13:27.590 --> 13:28.870
Someone after the Desireless Stone.

13:29.360 --> 13:30.270
Just like you?

13:33.630 --> 13:34.510
What are you doing?

13:34.870 --> 13:36.030
Leave now.

13:36.050 --> 13:37.730
It's not my father's birthday yet.

13:37.750 --> 13:39.380
If you don't leave, your death will come

13:39.410 --> 13:40.690
before your father's birthday.

13:43.740 --> 13:44.810
What do you mean by that?

13:44.840 --> 13:45.920
Make it clear,

13:45.950 --> 13:47.230
or I won't go with you.

13:57.040 --> 13:57.960
She's having…

14:00.450 --> 14:01.960
divine visions.

14:43.600 --> 14:44.670
Young Lord!

14:44.690 --> 14:46.050
Young Lord, how are you?

14:46.120 --> 14:46.930
Young Lord.

14:46.960 --> 14:48.320
You can't die, Young Lord.

14:48.360 --> 14:50.240
What should I do if you die?

14:50.270 --> 14:51.670
I'll take you back.

14:54.620 --> 14:56.580
What should I do?

14:59.720 --> 15:01.600
The fact that the Desireless Stone is in Shuo

15:01.630 --> 15:03.030
must not be discovered by the Eternals.

15:03.700 --> 15:05.580
I need to find a way to take it out

15:05.610 --> 15:07.010
before they find out.

15:07.660 --> 15:08.350
Oh, no.

15:08.370 --> 15:09.600
An Eternal is coming this way.

15:10.430 --> 15:11.280
It's too late.

15:11.300 --> 15:13.450
I can only hide her demon aura for now.

15:28.170 --> 15:28.930
Miss.

15:28.960 --> 15:29.800
What happened to you?

15:33.530 --> 15:35.150
How did you get so badly injured?

15:35.820 --> 15:37.250
I'll take you to a physician first.

15:37.280 --> 15:38.370
Excuse me.

15:58.000 --> 16:01.930
[Jihuai Clinic]

16:02.130 --> 16:03.080
Sir.

16:03.250 --> 16:04.360
Sir.

16:04.640 --> 16:05.550
She's gravely injured.

16:05.580 --> 16:06.750
Please save her.

16:07.670 --> 16:09.000
Her injury looks severe.

16:13.620 --> 16:14.570
Sir.

16:14.600 --> 16:15.560
How is she?

16:15.580 --> 16:16.770
The wound is severe,

16:16.800 --> 16:18.420
but fortunately, her vital organs are unharmed.

16:20.110 --> 16:21.070
That's a relief.

16:24.650 --> 16:25.580
The money is here.

16:25.610 --> 16:26.860
I have to leave now.

16:33.450 --> 16:34.240
What could be

16:34.240 --> 16:36.300
more important than your wife?

16:36.410 --> 16:37.720
She's so badly injured.

16:37.740 --> 16:39.000
Where are you going?

16:39.000 --> 16:40.410
She's not my wife.

16:41.080 --> 16:42.960
Whether she's your wife or not,

16:42.980 --> 16:44.410
her wound is under her clothes.

16:44.440 --> 16:46.050
I have to undress her to treat her.

16:46.070 --> 16:47.620
If you leave her here alone,

16:48.140 --> 16:50.110
her reputation may be stained.

16:50.130 --> 16:51.520
How am I going to explain it then?

16:51.550 --> 16:52.240
Hurry,

16:52.260 --> 16:53.350
take her to the inner room.

16:53.380 --> 16:54.620
She needs to be treated immediately,

16:54.640 --> 16:56.330
or she'll bleed to death.

16:56.760 --> 16:57.550
Hurry.

16:59.660 --> 17:00.450
Come with me.

17:27.329 --> 17:29.240
The problem in the city hasn't been solved.

17:29.530 --> 17:31.090
I can't stay here for too long.

17:35.280 --> 17:38.390
[Unbridled Pavilion]

17:48.240 --> 17:49.590
Why am I here?

17:49.610 --> 17:51.500
The Desireless Stone triggered divine power,

17:51.530 --> 17:52.450
showing you things

17:52.480 --> 17:54.240
that usually shouldn't be seen.

17:54.930 --> 17:56.100
Tell me.

17:56.130 --> 17:57.290
What did you see?

18:02.270 --> 18:03.050
Move!

18:05.270 --> 18:07.210
That's my family's abandoned courtyard.

18:07.570 --> 18:09.640
Why are there so many mad people locked there?

18:11.000 --> 18:12.490
I can't remember clearly.

18:13.260 --> 18:14.500
Just blurry images

18:14.530 --> 18:15.640
with a lot of people in them.

18:16.080 --> 18:17.820
Why did the Desireless Stone

18:18.160 --> 18:19.120
show me those things?

18:19.150 --> 18:20.520
I've told you before,

18:21.030 --> 18:22.180
to activate the Desireless Stone,

18:22.200 --> 18:24.090
one needs to gather the Five Contemplations.

18:24.120 --> 18:26.050
As a divine object, it has its own mind.

18:26.070 --> 18:27.390
What it showed you must be

18:27.420 --> 18:28.860
the key to gathering Contemplations.

18:29.970 --> 18:31.730
I'll stay here and watch you

18:31.790 --> 18:33.460
until you recall everything clearly.

18:33.920 --> 18:36.030
I can't remember it all at once.

18:36.630 --> 18:38.230
Why don't you tell me first

18:38.250 --> 18:40.170
if the visions the Stone showed me

18:40.200 --> 18:41.480
are illusions

18:41.500 --> 18:42.370
or reality?

18:42.930 --> 18:43.820
Bai Shuo,

18:44.780 --> 18:47.260
playing dumb won't do you any good.

18:47.290 --> 18:48.250
You misunderstood.

18:48.810 --> 18:50.400
I'm not playing dumb

18:50.400 --> 18:51.960
when it comes to the Desireless Stone.

18:51.960 --> 18:53.420
I'm just a human.

18:53.440 --> 18:55.170
How could I know the powers of a divine object?

18:59.290 --> 19:00.600
What the Desireless Stone shows

19:01.260 --> 19:02.550
are things that haven't happened yet

19:02.550 --> 19:04.350
but will surely happen in the future.

19:04.890 --> 19:06.460
To obtain the Contemplations,

19:06.480 --> 19:09.000
those things must happen exactly as shown.

19:10.610 --> 19:11.700
Anyway,

19:11.720 --> 19:13.330
you just need to recall what you saw.

19:13.710 --> 19:15.190
I'll handle the rest.

19:15.680 --> 19:17.440
Things that haven't happened yet

19:17.470 --> 19:19.310
but will surely happen in the future?

19:19.770 --> 19:21.570
Does that mean everything I saw

19:21.590 --> 19:22.550
will happen?

19:23.380 --> 19:24.850
I'm not sure if he's a foe or a friend.

19:24.880 --> 19:26.390
He may not genuinely want to help me.

19:26.410 --> 19:28.340
I need to look into this myself.

19:31.880 --> 19:33.810
My head really hurts.

19:33.830 --> 19:34.730
The more you ask,

19:34.750 --> 19:36.030
the worse it gets.

19:36.050 --> 19:37.310
Let me go home to think about it.

19:38.110 --> 19:39.530
Bai Shuo.

19:40.650 --> 19:41.970
Those who deceive me

19:42.670 --> 19:44.100
don't end well.

19:45.960 --> 19:47.090
Don't worry.

19:47.630 --> 19:49.790
There's something really important I haven't done.

19:49.990 --> 19:50.960
I value my life very much.

19:51.290 --> 19:52.890
If I remember anything,

19:52.910 --> 19:53.940
I'll tell you.

20:07.060 --> 20:07.820
Hurry.

20:07.840 --> 20:09.060
Put them under control!

20:15.720 --> 20:16.470
Open the door!

20:42.680 --> 20:43.270
Move!

20:44.110 --> 20:44.980
Move!

21:06.290 --> 21:07.090
Master,

21:08.450 --> 21:09.780
I followed Bai Shuo

21:09.810 --> 21:11.240
and saw her go to an abandoned courtyard.

21:11.260 --> 21:13.020
There were a lot of strange people locked up there.

21:13.050 --> 21:13.920
They seemed

21:13.940 --> 21:15.550
to be poisoned with the Nether Poison.

21:15.580 --> 21:18.050
Cold Spring Palace sent Fu Ling to capture Bai Shuo,

21:18.080 --> 21:20.050
so the Nether Poison must be their doing too.

21:20.070 --> 21:21.180
Then,

21:21.210 --> 21:23.130
should we take Bai Shuo and leave the city?

21:23.880 --> 21:24.860
No need.

21:24.880 --> 21:26.970
The Desireless Stone has shown Bai Shuo something,

21:27.530 --> 21:29.130
and it's tied to those poisoned.

21:29.960 --> 21:32.000
Whatever the first Contemplation is,

21:32.030 --> 21:33.950
it's bound to show up in Ning'an City.

21:35.210 --> 21:36.520
All we need to do

21:37.910 --> 21:38.950
is wait.

22:15.190 --> 22:16.910
Chong Zhao from Lanling Sect.

22:17.330 --> 22:18.680
It's him.

22:22.900 --> 22:23.870
Miss,

22:23.900 --> 22:25.140
you're finally awake.

22:26.110 --> 22:27.070
Where is he?

22:27.100 --> 22:27.690
He?

22:28.550 --> 22:29.400
You mean

22:29.400 --> 22:31.310
the gentleman who brought you here yesterday?

22:31.550 --> 22:32.830
He said he had urgent business

22:32.860 --> 22:33.820
and left.

22:33.840 --> 22:35.150
He's paid for your treatment.

22:35.180 --> 22:35.910
Miss,

22:35.930 --> 22:37.240
don't worry.

22:38.550 --> 22:40.220
Your wound is quite deep.

22:40.240 --> 22:42.290
You'll need plenty of time to recover.

22:42.580 --> 22:44.370
So, it was you who treated me?

22:44.400 --> 22:45.440
Yes, indeed.

22:45.460 --> 22:46.550
Don't worry.

22:46.580 --> 22:48.180
When I applied the medicine last night,

22:48.210 --> 22:49.960
that gentleman was right beside me.

22:50.530 --> 22:51.920
Even if anyone asks,

22:51.950 --> 22:53.880
it won't affect your reputation.

22:54.930 --> 22:56.400
Miss, remember to take your medicine.

22:56.590 --> 22:57.790
Have a good rest.

23:03.770 --> 23:04.890
It won't affect my reputation.

23:04.910 --> 23:06.220
The dead don't talk.

23:16.120 --> 23:18.980
I saw that scholar among the sick today.

23:19.010 --> 23:20.780
It seems the visions from the Desireless Stone

23:20.800 --> 23:21.950
are indeed prophecies.

23:23.730 --> 23:25.350
Fan Yue can't be trusted.

23:25.370 --> 23:26.370
From the moment I met him,

23:26.400 --> 23:28.040
nothing has gone smoothly.

23:28.060 --> 23:29.030
I don't know if his story

23:29.030 --> 23:30.350
about the benefactor is true or not.

23:30.920 --> 23:32.360
It's hard to say whether those mad people

23:32.380 --> 23:33.730
have something to do with him.

23:34.260 --> 23:35.540
If chaos breaks out in the city,

23:35.860 --> 23:36.510
my father,

23:36.510 --> 23:38.720
Zhao, and I will very likely die.

23:39.510 --> 23:40.260
No.

23:40.370 --> 23:42.520
I must find a way to get my father and Zhao out of here.

23:42.760 --> 23:43.800
If we stay,

23:43.820 --> 23:44.760
-we're all doomed.
-Hurry. Hurry.

23:44.830 --> 23:45.830
Keep moving!

23:46.300 --> 23:47.080
Fall in!

23:54.600 --> 23:55.560
Are you ready?

23:55.590 --> 23:56.360
Yes!

23:56.390 --> 23:56.990
Father!

23:57.720 --> 23:58.290
Bai Yu.

23:58.310 --> 23:58.960
Go to the south of the city

23:58.960 --> 24:00.160
and control the sick there.

24:00.280 --> 24:00.800
Got it.

24:01.720 --> 24:02.640
Father, listen to me.

24:02.670 --> 24:03.700
Shuo, you listen to me.

24:04.450 --> 24:05.620
Behind the hidden door in my room,

24:05.650 --> 24:06.400
there are the valuables

24:06.400 --> 24:07.500
I've saved over the years

24:07.530 --> 24:09.180
and also some dowry your mother left for you.

24:09.200 --> 24:10.070
Pack whatever is light,

24:10.110 --> 24:11.000
find Zhao,

24:11.000 --> 24:12.070
and leave the city tonight.

24:12.100 --> 24:13.680
Father, what are you talking about?

24:13.710 --> 24:14.790
-You...
-Governor!

24:15.740 --> 24:16.460
Governor.

24:16.480 --> 24:17.690
There are mad people in the west of the city too.

24:17.720 --> 24:19.390
Wang and the others can't hold on any longer.

24:19.460 --> 24:20.310
Got it.

24:20.330 --> 24:21.000
Wait for me outside.

24:21.070 --> 24:21.830
Yes!

24:23.580 --> 24:24.760
Shuo.

24:24.810 --> 24:25.530
Remember,

24:25.560 --> 24:27.160
leave before tonight.

24:27.180 --> 24:28.450
There will be great chaos in the city.

24:28.480 --> 24:29.690
Staying here is dangerous.

24:30.550 --> 24:31.210
Father.

24:32.660 --> 24:33.530
Father!

24:41.130 --> 24:42.400
The demon poison in the city

24:42.430 --> 24:44.180
is definitely related to Unbridled Pavilion.

24:44.500 --> 24:45.690
I must get to the bottom of this.

24:47.300 --> 24:49.040
My goods are great.

24:49.070 --> 24:50.760
Stop hanging around outside.

24:50.780 --> 24:52.130
Go home now.

24:52.150 --> 24:52.950
What happened?

24:53.000 --> 24:54.790
Something terrible happened in the south and the west of the city.

24:54.790 --> 24:56.310
You've heard about the recent disease, right?

24:56.460 --> 24:58.510
It's already spreading through the south and west.

24:58.530 --> 24:59.830
It's getting out of control!

25:00.270 --> 25:00.830
This…

25:00.830 --> 25:02.000
Who knows if those mad people

25:02.000 --> 25:03.350
will show up here?

25:03.350 --> 25:04.570
What should we do?

25:04.640 --> 25:05.070
Go home.

25:05.070 --> 25:06.070
Hurry up, go, go, go!

25:19.180 --> 25:19.940
Young Lord.

25:19.960 --> 25:21.330
I've done a great job, haven't I?

25:21.360 --> 25:23.530
I even managed to fool that Eternal called Chong Zhao.

25:24.240 --> 25:26.090
I didn't run away last night.

25:26.120 --> 25:28.020
I went back to the palace to get medicine for you.

25:28.040 --> 25:28.890
Here, take it.

25:28.920 --> 25:30.050
You'll feel better after taking it.

25:33.390 --> 25:35.400
Why aren't you speaking?

25:35.770 --> 25:37.320
Don't you want to praise me?

25:38.000 --> 25:39.160
Grand Master always says

25:39.160 --> 25:41.060
the Eternals can't amount to much.

25:41.240 --> 25:42.840
Today, I finally understand.

25:43.080 --> 25:45.240
Chong Zhao, the head disciple of Lanling,

25:45.260 --> 25:47.240
couldn't recognize danger in the face of it.

25:47.610 --> 25:48.640
He went through so much trouble

25:48.640 --> 25:50.720
to save someone he barely knows.

25:51.100 --> 25:52.560
How foolish.

25:52.960 --> 25:54.120
Young Lord,

25:54.160 --> 25:56.050
why do I feel like you're praising him?

25:56.070 --> 25:57.030
Praising?

25:58.990 --> 26:01.450
Why are you looking at me like that?

26:01.470 --> 26:03.640
My wound hasn't healed yet, but I still have things to do.

26:03.670 --> 26:04.700
I need to borrow your demon power.

26:05.350 --> 26:06.180
How much do you need?

26:06.200 --> 26:07.200
All of it.

26:07.630 --> 26:09.320
Then be careful not to drain it.

26:57.510 --> 26:58.720
Boys, be careful.

26:58.720 --> 26:59.680
Don't hurt anyone!

26:59.680 --> 27:00.590
Yes!

27:40.350 --> 27:41.110
Governor!

27:46.280 --> 27:47.040
Father!

27:50.630 --> 27:52.320
The master the Desireless Stone chose.

27:52.340 --> 27:53.210
Bai Shuo,

27:53.240 --> 27:54.610
I'm curious to see

27:54.630 --> 27:56.190
what makes you so special.

28:01.840 --> 28:02.800
Don't hurt them!

28:05.670 --> 28:06.590
You demon,

28:06.610 --> 28:07.890
how dare you cause havoc here?

28:17.140 --> 28:18.350
It's you.

28:18.500 --> 28:20.170
I should thank you

28:20.200 --> 28:21.770
for your kind help

28:21.790 --> 28:22.980
in saving my life.

28:23.010 --> 28:24.620
Had I known you were a demon,

28:24.640 --> 28:26.270
I should've killed you last night.

28:26.300 --> 28:28.060
But it was also you who hurried to save me

28:28.110 --> 28:28.720
last night.

28:28.720 --> 28:30.140
I meant to save a human, not a demon!

28:30.170 --> 28:31.490
What poison have you spread

28:31.510 --> 28:32.710
in Ning'an City?

28:32.740 --> 28:34.220
You deny you saved me,

28:34.270 --> 28:35.750
but I won't forget your kindness.

28:35.780 --> 28:38.150
This is the long-lost Nether Poison of the Demon Race.

28:38.200 --> 28:39.680
It has resurfaced now.

28:39.710 --> 28:40.990
Mr. Eternal,

28:41.010 --> 28:42.290
do you like

28:42.390 --> 28:43.530
this thank-you gift?

29:03.080 --> 29:03.800
Father!

29:04.740 --> 29:05.390
Father.

29:10.440 --> 29:12.480
Someone, help me carry my father back.

29:17.200 --> 29:19.350
Go help her! Why are you hesitating?

29:22.840 --> 29:24.630
He's your governor.

29:24.650 --> 29:26.970
He's become like this to save you,

29:27.000 --> 29:28.410
yet you're scared of him?

29:28.980 --> 29:30.180
Listen.

29:30.210 --> 29:31.780
My father won't become like that.

29:54.960 --> 29:55.810
Father!

30:04.530 --> 30:05.660
Give me the antidote!

30:05.680 --> 30:07.280
This wasn't your attitude

30:07.310 --> 30:08.620
when you saved me last night.

30:08.640 --> 30:09.330
Father.

30:09.650 --> 30:10.690
Lady Shuo, don't go over.

30:10.720 --> 30:12.050
He'll bite you.

30:12.070 --> 30:13.070
Father, wake up.

30:13.090 --> 30:14.300
I'm Shuo!

30:22.920 --> 30:23.510
Father.

30:23.880 --> 30:24.530
Father.

30:33.780 --> 30:34.550
Father.

30:35.020 --> 30:35.960
Wake up.

30:36.470 --> 30:37.900
I'm your daughter.

30:45.530 --> 30:46.930
Drop the act.

30:47.600 --> 30:48.840
Demons caused chaos among humans.

30:48.860 --> 30:49.640
You deserve death!

30:49.930 --> 30:51.930
You Eternals claim to uphold justice

30:51.960 --> 30:53.440
and protect humans,

30:53.460 --> 30:54.570
but look at them.

30:55.300 --> 30:56.860
Humans are weak, useless,

30:56.890 --> 30:58.160
and hypocritical.

30:58.180 --> 31:00.380
When disaster strikes, they only care about themselves.

31:00.400 --> 31:02.070
What's so worth protecting

31:02.100 --> 31:04.100
in a race like this?

31:04.120 --> 31:05.360
Nonsense!

31:05.930 --> 31:06.930
Humans may be weak,

31:06.960 --> 31:08.100
but their nature is pure and good.

31:08.130 --> 31:09.570
If not for your Nether Poison,

31:09.590 --> 31:11.150
how could these people have ended up like this?

31:11.180 --> 31:12.940
Pure and good?

31:12.960 --> 31:14.410
Ning'an has fallen,

31:14.440 --> 31:16.030
and Bai Xun's been poisoned too.

31:16.050 --> 31:17.570
I'd love to see

31:17.600 --> 31:19.470
in this hellish world,

31:19.490 --> 31:20.890
where all that

31:20.920 --> 31:22.330
pure goodness is.

31:22.350 --> 31:23.790
Cut the crap!

31:23.820 --> 31:24.840
Give me the antidote.

31:24.860 --> 31:26.170
The Nether Poison is incurable.

31:26.200 --> 31:28.240
You have to kill all the mad people.

31:28.260 --> 31:29.000
Otherwise,

31:29.020 --> 31:29.990
as long as they're alive,

31:30.010 --> 31:31.000
they'll stay mad.

31:31.480 --> 31:32.150
Fine.

31:32.540 --> 31:33.740
If you don't give it to me,

31:33.770 --> 31:35.090
I'll trade your life

31:35.110 --> 31:37.060
for the antidote with your master.

31:37.080 --> 31:39.090
You think too highly of me.

31:39.430 --> 31:41.510
The Master of Bright Moon Palace is ruthless

31:41.540 --> 31:43.530
and wouldn't care about my life.

31:43.560 --> 31:44.940
The Master of Bright Moon Palace?

31:47.370 --> 31:48.240
With your strength,

31:48.260 --> 31:49.660
you can't defeat my master.

31:50.540 --> 31:51.350
If you want to live…

31:51.350 --> 31:51.920
Flower demon again.

31:51.920 --> 31:52.830
Get out of Ning'an City.

31:52.830 --> 31:54.560
What's her connection to that top courtesan?

31:54.790 --> 31:55.880
The Master of Bright Moon Palace?

31:56.060 --> 31:57.230
The owner of Unbridled Pavilion!

32:14.260 --> 32:16.200
We've stocked up on wound medicine,

32:16.680 --> 32:18.740
but why can't I find any when I need it?

32:25.290 --> 32:25.960
Look.

32:25.960 --> 32:26.830
It looks just like my father, right?

32:27.170 --> 32:28.860
This is the figurine you've spent days making

32:28.890 --> 32:30.280
for your father's birthday?

32:30.300 --> 32:32.150
Without the governor's armor,

32:32.200 --> 32:34.480
Uncle Bai probably can't even recognize himself.

32:34.500 --> 32:35.850
I've never done this before.

32:36.330 --> 32:37.960
My hands hurt from shaping it.

32:37.980 --> 32:39.630
This is the best one I made.

32:39.660 --> 32:40.770
Tomorrow is his birthday.

32:40.790 --> 32:42.320
Do you think he'll like it?

32:42.340 --> 32:43.450
Uncle Bai will surely love

32:43.480 --> 32:45.080
anything you give him.

32:45.400 --> 32:46.120
Bai Shuo!

32:46.770 --> 32:47.580
Father.

32:48.760 --> 32:49.520
Look.

32:49.540 --> 32:50.630
Get that away!

32:58.270 --> 32:59.590
I warned you not to go to

32:59.610 --> 33:01.130
the burial ground outside the city.

33:01.160 --> 33:02.130
Why did you go again?

33:02.400 --> 33:04.900
That's where Xi and I were saved by the immortal.

33:04.930 --> 33:05.780
Why can't I go there?

33:05.800 --> 33:06.990
There are no immortals!

33:07.400 --> 33:08.480
I told you!

33:09.440 --> 33:10.680
You're the daughter of the city governor.

33:10.710 --> 33:11.990
You should know your place.

33:12.010 --> 33:12.970
If Xi were here,

33:13.000 --> 33:14.650
she wouldn't be as naughty as you!

33:14.670 --> 33:16.300
Do you always wish

33:16.350 --> 33:18.350
it had been me taken by the Taoist

33:18.370 --> 33:19.780
instead of Xi?

33:20.590 --> 33:21.950
You little brat.

33:22.000 --> 33:23.680
Bai Xun, I hate you!

33:23.710 --> 33:25.230
Shuo, Shuo!

33:38.740 --> 33:40.600
Since you've glued it back together,

33:41.200 --> 33:42.310
why didn't you tell me?

33:43.000 --> 33:44.440
Lady Shuo, stop searching.

33:44.440 --> 33:45.870
Wound medicine won't work on the madness.

33:52.500 --> 33:53.670
Father,

33:53.700 --> 33:54.970
hang in there.

33:54.990 --> 33:56.340
Wait for me to come back.

33:56.950 --> 33:57.800
Bai Yu.

33:57.900 --> 33:58.940
Take care of my father.

33:58.960 --> 34:00.820
I'll definitely find a way to cure him.

34:02.310 --> 34:03.150
Lady Shuo.

34:04.100 --> 34:05.270
It's dangerous outside!

34:23.070 --> 34:24.949
What a distinguished guest.

34:24.969 --> 34:26.010
What?

34:26.040 --> 34:27.000
Are you here for drinks?

34:27.020 --> 34:28.270
The rules between our two races still stand.

34:28.300 --> 34:29.900
In the demon territory, how you fight among yourselves

34:29.920 --> 34:31.340
is none of our concern.

34:31.360 --> 34:33.110
But why did you come to mess with humans?

34:33.139 --> 34:35.050
What nonsense are you talking about?

34:36.120 --> 34:37.120
Let him finish.

34:37.920 --> 34:38.949
Three days ago,

34:38.969 --> 34:41.290
your top courtesan spread poison throughout the city.

34:41.310 --> 34:44.100
Today, your underlings used demon magic to control the mad people.

34:44.130 --> 34:45.900
What do you want,

34:46.110 --> 34:47.460
Master of Bright Moon Palace?

34:47.489 --> 34:50.260
You can't even see such an obvious frame-up.

34:50.280 --> 34:51.600
How foolish you are.

34:52.290 --> 34:54.360
Lady Fu Ling from Cold Spring Palace

34:54.380 --> 34:57.310
specializes in flower demons' teleportation and uses the Cloud Fire Bow.

34:57.340 --> 34:58.860
You're so ill-informed.

34:58.880 --> 35:00.270
Work on that.

35:11.220 --> 35:12.490
You said it's a frame-up,

35:12.520 --> 35:13.600
but why should I believe you?

35:13.620 --> 35:15.190
Do I need you to believe me?

35:15.220 --> 35:17.580
Right now, the city is in chaos, and the people are suffering.

35:17.600 --> 35:19.730
I don't have time to argue with you about that.

35:19.760 --> 35:21.200
The Nether Poison is from demons.

35:21.220 --> 35:22.290
Give me the antidote!

35:22.410 --> 35:24.630
So you still care about the people, huh?

35:40.920 --> 35:42.170
Shuo.

35:42.190 --> 35:43.500
The blade should face the enemy;

35:43.530 --> 35:44.660
the back should face yourself.

35:45.690 --> 35:47.130
Remember this:

35:48.000 --> 35:49.090
never

35:49.110 --> 35:51.380
hold the blade to your own people.

36:01.510 --> 36:03.630
If you truly cared about the people,

36:03.720 --> 36:06.670
you should've reported the Nether Poison to Lanling Sect long ago.

36:06.760 --> 36:08.100
But why haven't we

36:08.120 --> 36:09.470
seen any help from Lanling?

36:09.490 --> 36:10.970
You want to cure the poisoned,

36:11.000 --> 36:12.690
but you wouldn't report it to Lanling.

36:13.360 --> 36:14.820
Why is that?

36:15.460 --> 36:17.120
Let me guess.

36:17.650 --> 36:18.960
It's because

36:19.760 --> 36:21.360
you're afraid.

36:22.970 --> 36:24.800
You're afraid Lanling Sect will find out

36:24.800 --> 36:26.360
that the Desireless Stone is inside Bai Shuo,

36:26.390 --> 36:28.390
and that they'll kill her to prevent future problems.

36:30.650 --> 36:32.250
They say demons are evil,

36:33.070 --> 36:34.950
but I think you Eternals are far greedier,

36:34.970 --> 36:36.340
wanting everything.

36:36.360 --> 36:37.470
You care for the commoners?

36:38.480 --> 36:39.670
What a joke.

36:47.810 --> 36:49.160
Help!

37:02.040 --> 37:03.650
Ms. Bai, you came at the right time.

37:05.000 --> 37:07.560
I was just discussing your life and death

37:07.580 --> 37:09.100
with Mr. Chong Zhao, an Eternal.

37:33.650 --> 37:34.730
Is what he said

37:35.480 --> 37:36.590
true?

37:39.730 --> 37:40.770
You're an Eternal?

37:44.010 --> 37:45.530
You're actually an Eternal?

37:48.960 --> 37:50.110
Say something!

37:54.320 --> 37:55.240
Ms. Bai.

37:56.070 --> 37:58.670
My restaurant welcomes humans but not Eternals.

37:59.090 --> 38:00.490
If you have family matters to discuss,

38:01.010 --> 38:02.340
please take them home.

38:02.880 --> 38:05.360
Don't be an annoying sight here

38:05.390 --> 38:07.200
and disturb my peace.

38:07.220 --> 38:08.220
Wait.

38:08.510 --> 38:09.400
I need to talk to you.

38:09.430 --> 38:10.580
Come with me.

38:12.980 --> 38:14.040
Master.

38:14.200 --> 38:15.600
You just let them go?

38:15.620 --> 38:16.810
Bai Shuo came here

38:17.200 --> 38:18.430
for Bai Xun.

38:18.460 --> 38:19.620
Eternals

38:20.150 --> 38:21.550
can't cure the demon poison.

38:21.570 --> 38:23.420
She'll come back to beg me eventually.

38:24.080 --> 38:25.740
When she comes,

38:26.180 --> 38:28.700
she has to meet whatever conditions I have.

38:37.280 --> 38:38.160
Shuo.

38:38.180 --> 38:39.410
Hide here.

38:39.440 --> 38:41.480
Once the demons in the city are killed and the chaos settles,

38:41.500 --> 38:42.310
I'll come to you.

38:47.300 --> 38:48.450
Why did you lie to me?

38:49.300 --> 38:50.530
You know all along

38:50.560 --> 38:52.250
that the only thing I've ever wanted

38:52.270 --> 38:53.500
since a child is immortality.

38:53.530 --> 38:55.260
Everyone laughed at me

38:55.280 --> 38:56.320
and called me a fool.

38:56.360 --> 38:56.880
For the past ten years,

38:56.880 --> 38:58.840
you've watched as people mocked

38:58.840 --> 38:59.880
and ridiculed me

38:59.880 --> 39:01.710
and watched me argue with my father over and over.

39:01.710 --> 39:04.090
Why did you never tell me you were an Eternal?

39:05.440 --> 39:06.550
Answer me!

39:07.960 --> 39:09.150
The rules of the Eternals forbid me.

39:09.730 --> 39:10.820
Shuo.

39:10.910 --> 39:12.120
I can't tell you.

39:12.660 --> 39:13.750
The Eternals' rules?

39:14.770 --> 39:16.080
Are those rules

39:16.960 --> 39:18.690
more important than the family

39:18.720 --> 39:20.720
with whom you've spent ten years?

39:20.740 --> 39:22.940
How could you watch me act like a fool

39:22.970 --> 39:24.640
without doing anything?

39:24.870 --> 39:26.620
When you saw me chasing after those swindlers

39:26.650 --> 39:27.650
and calling them immortals,

39:27.710 --> 39:28.880
what were you thinking?

39:29.370 --> 39:30.940
Did you think I was laughable?

39:31.000 --> 39:32.830
I never once thought that.

39:32.860 --> 39:33.760
Since my parents died,

39:33.760 --> 39:34.840
I've truly considered you and Uncle Bai

39:34.840 --> 39:35.910
my family.

39:35.940 --> 39:38.140
I've never thought of mocking you.

39:38.160 --> 39:39.120
Family?

39:40.550 --> 39:41.840
Back at Unbridled Pavilion,

39:42.210 --> 39:44.120
you and Fan Yue were acting strange.

39:44.140 --> 39:45.290
I had doubts,

39:45.960 --> 39:47.870
but I didn't want to doubt you,

39:47.950 --> 39:49.600
because you're Chong Zhao,

39:49.650 --> 39:51.490
someone I consider family.

39:53.210 --> 39:56.480
You've always known I hate being lied to,

39:57.580 --> 40:00.160
yet the biggest liar around me

40:01.150 --> 40:01.960
is you.

40:05.110 --> 40:06.070
Shuo,

40:06.840 --> 40:07.820
I didn't mean

40:08.550 --> 40:10.160
to lie to you.

40:11.880 --> 40:12.550
Alright.

40:13.360 --> 40:15.000
Let's say you were bound by the rules

40:15.000 --> 40:15.880
and couldn't tell me.

40:17.290 --> 40:18.630
But since you're an Eternal,

40:18.850 --> 40:20.170
you must have a way to save my father,

40:20.200 --> 40:20.950
right?

40:22.900 --> 40:24.010
You're young.

40:24.040 --> 40:25.410
You may not be powerful,

40:25.430 --> 40:26.830
but you must have a master

40:26.870 --> 40:27.830
and a sect.

40:28.320 --> 40:29.550
Go find them.

40:29.550 --> 40:31.070
They must be powerful enough to have a solution,

40:31.070 --> 40:31.800
right?

40:33.030 --> 40:33.920
Shuo,

40:35.440 --> 40:36.400
that's a demon poison.

40:36.400 --> 40:37.030
The Eternal Race…

40:38.160 --> 40:39.560
The Eternal Race can't cure it.

40:44.400 --> 40:47.410
♫I remember that moonlit night♫

40:46.870 --> 40:48.470
Even if my master comes,

40:48.160 --> 40:51.660
♫The flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime♫

40:50.630 --> 40:51.590
there's nothing that can be done.

40:51.830 --> 40:55.300
♫I remember that word of concern♫

40:55.820 --> 40:59.080
♫But unfortunately, I didn't get to answer♫

40:57.070 --> 40:58.430
We've lived together for ten years.

40:59.140 --> 41:00.660
My father treated you like his own son,

40:59.650 --> 41:02.430
♫I remember that drop of tear♫

41:02.000 --> 41:03.880
yet you're telling me there's nothing that can be done.

41:03.230 --> 41:06.490
♫It dried in the wind♫

41:04.830 --> 41:06.100
Eternals are supposed to protect the people,

41:06.620 --> 41:08.530
but who exactly are they protecting?

41:07.080 --> 41:08.880
♫The one in the autumn wind♫

41:09.110 --> 41:09.630
Fine.

41:09.350 --> 41:13.010
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

41:11.050 --> 41:12.820
Since the Eternal Race can't do anything about it

41:12.980 --> 41:14.100
and can't save my father,

41:13.720 --> 41:17.050
♫That year, that year♫

41:14.420 --> 41:15.860
I'll go find someone who can.

41:16.480 --> 41:17.510
Shuo.

41:17.980 --> 41:21.090
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

41:18.110 --> 41:18.670
Fan Yue is a demon.

41:18.670 --> 41:19.760
He won't help you.

41:20.400 --> 41:21.030
He approached you because...

41:21.050 --> 41:22.900
I don't care why he approached me.

41:21.530 --> 41:24.970
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

41:23.490 --> 41:25.140
Neither do I care whether he's an Eternal

41:25.170 --> 41:26.290
or a demon.

41:26.030 --> 41:28.440
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

41:27.300 --> 41:28.840
As long as he can save my father,

41:29.220 --> 41:32.480
♫That year, that year♫

41:29.400 --> 41:30.250
I'll trust him.

41:33.310 --> 41:36.330
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

41:34.830 --> 41:35.840
The Desireless Stone is in your body.

41:35.840 --> 41:37.550
If you go back, both Eternals and demons will come after you.

41:36.970 --> 41:40.000
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

41:38.000 --> 41:39.150
Stay here for now.

41:39.150 --> 41:40.480
After the demons in the city are wiped out,

41:40.480 --> 41:41.150
I'll send you to a place

41:41.150 --> 41:42.920
where neither Eternals nor demons can find you.

41:41.220 --> 41:43.120
♫Layer after layer♫

41:42.920 --> 41:44.550
My father is waiting for me in the city.

41:44.550 --> 41:45.800
Where do you want me to run off to?

41:44.660 --> 41:47.630
♫Another year passed♫

41:45.800 --> 41:47.000
I'll save Uncle Bai.

41:47.000 --> 41:48.800
How are you going to save him?

41:51.510 --> 41:53.590
You said the Eternals can't cure the demon poison.

41:54.350 --> 41:55.570
Then tell me,

41:55.590 --> 41:57.170
even if the demons are driven out,

41:57.880 --> 41:59.320
how will the Eternals deal with my father

41:59.360 --> 42:00.940
and the mad people in the city?

41:59.970 --> 42:03.280
♫I remember that moonlit night♫

42:01.000 --> 42:03.690
Will they kill them all to prevent future problems?

42:03.900 --> 42:06.260
♫The flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime♫

42:03.970 --> 42:06.570
Or lock them away like animals until they die?

42:06.840 --> 42:11.080
♫I remember that word of concern♫

42:08.440 --> 42:10.630
You don't have a solution.

42:11.380 --> 42:12.900
And neither does

42:11.780 --> 42:14.760
♫But unfortunately, I didn't get to answer♫

42:12.930 --> 42:14.700
the Eternal Race.

42:14.720 --> 42:16.160
My father is still waiting for me.

42:15.250 --> 42:18.120
♫I remember that drop of tear♫

42:17.150 --> 42:18.230
Let me go.

42:19.060 --> 42:22.270
♫It dried in the wind♫

42:19.250 --> 42:21.630
I'll ask my master and the other leaders for help.

42:22.600 --> 42:23.990
Stay here for now.

42:22.920 --> 42:24.480
♫The one in the autumn wind♫

42:24.020 --> 42:25.310
Even if it's not for anything else,

42:24.980 --> 42:28.650
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

42:26.220 --> 42:28.410
you've been seeking immortality for ten years to repay your debt.

42:29.090 --> 42:31.050
You need to stay alive

42:29.760 --> 42:33.090
♫That year, that year♫

42:31.080 --> 42:32.810
for the immortal who saved you.

42:33.740 --> 42:36.630
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

42:35.360 --> 42:36.760
I wish to repay my debt,

42:37.540 --> 42:40.880
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

42:38.230 --> 42:39.480
but if repaying it means

42:39.920 --> 42:41.960
abandoning my family and morals

42:41.800 --> 42:44.270
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

42:42.710 --> 42:45.280
and surviving like a rat in a gutter,

42:44.930 --> 42:48.390
♫That year, that year♫

42:46.340 --> 42:47.820
then I'll hate myself for it,

42:47.880 --> 42:49.110
and I'm sure the immortal

42:48.770 --> 42:51.950
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

42:49.950 --> 42:51.760
who saved me would too.

42:52.480 --> 42:55.720
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

42:52.800 --> 42:53.880
Chong Zhao.

42:54.570 --> 42:56.490
I'll say this one last time.

42:57.060 --> 42:58.990
♫Layer after layer♫

42:57.480 --> 42:59.280
Let me go back.

42:59.280 --> 43:00.630
Don't make me hate you.

43:00.420 --> 43:03.380
♫Another year passed♫

43:08.950 --> 43:12.440
♫Another year passed♫

43:15.510 --> 43:16.510
Sorry.

43:17.940 --> 43:19.790
I have no choice but to keep you here.

43:20.550 --> 43:21.280
The Human Race can't

43:21.280 --> 43:23.190
resolve the chaos in Ning'an.

43:21.670 --> 43:25.090
♫That year, that year♫

43:24.100 --> 43:25.400
I won't let you die,

43:25.920 --> 43:28.670
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

43:26.220 --> 43:28.130
and I'll protect Uncle Bai.

43:29.630 --> 43:32.940
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

43:31.730 --> 43:32.480
Chong Zhao.

43:33.320 --> 43:34.110
Chong Zhao!

43:34.200 --> 43:36.350
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

43:34.480 --> 43:36.420
Come back, let me out!

43:37.020 --> 43:40.430
♫That year, that year♫

43:37.230 --> 43:38.000
Chong Zhao!

43:39.070 --> 43:39.840
Chong Zhao!

43:41.060 --> 43:44.270
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

43:41.310 --> 43:42.870
Maybe after today,

43:44.070 --> 43:45.880
we'll never return to how we were before.

43:44.930 --> 43:47.920
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

43:45.880 --> 43:46.840
Chong Zhao!

43:47.710 --> 43:49.220
-But Shuo...
-Chong Zhao!

43:48.990 --> 43:51.090
♫Layer after layer♫

43:49.280 --> 43:50.670
Let me out! Chong Zhao!

43:50.670 --> 43:52.070
To me,

43:52.730 --> 43:55.440
♫Another year passed♫

43:53.210 --> 43:54.650
you staying alive is more important.

43:59.210 --> 44:00.360
It's you.

44:00.380 --> 44:01.950
The top courtesan of Unbridled Pavilion?

44:00.890 --> 44:04.750
♫Another year passed♫

44:02.330 --> 44:04.410
The Master of Bright Moon Palace is ruthless

44:04.430 --> 44:06.140
and wouldn't care about my life.

44:06.690 --> 44:07.570
With your strength,

44:07.600 --> 44:08.960
you can't defeat my master.

44:08.980 --> 44:11.880
If you want to live, get out of Ning'an City.

44:11.910 --> 44:14.060
Lady Fu Ling from Cold Spring Palace

44:14.080 --> 44:16.910
specializes in flower demons' teleportation and uses the Cloud Fire Bow.

44:16.930 --> 44:18.530
You're so ill-informed.

44:18.560 --> 44:19.400
Work on that.

44:19.420 --> 44:21.460
They're all demons, each claiming their side of the story.

44:21.490 --> 44:23.740
Who should I trust?

44:23.760 --> 44:24.920
It seems that

44:24.960 --> 44:27.340
the demon girl is very likely the top courtesan

44:27.530 --> 44:29.200
or connected to Cold Spring Palace.

44:29.570 --> 44:32.290
The Eternals can't fight Bright Moon and Cold Spring at once.

44:32.320 --> 44:34.440
I need to figure out who the real enemy is.

44:34.460 --> 44:35.390
The key

44:35.420 --> 44:37.430
lies with that demon girl.
